---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<section class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl text-white">
            Comunidades aliadas 
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-xl text-gray-400">
            Las comunidades nos hacen crecer más como personas, nos impulsan a adentrarnos a los desconocido pero no solos, acompañados de gente con la misma pasión.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-beetwen justify-items-center">

              
                    <Image
                        src="/LogisticsHackathon/communities/ASCM_LOGOS_STUDENTFORUM_COLOR_W_UPIICSA.png"
                        alt="ASCM"
                        width={200}
                        height={100}
                        class="h-24 w-full object-contain transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105"
                    />
              

                
                    <Image
                        src="/LogisticsHackathon/communities/image.png"
                        alt="Binary Brains"
                        width={180}
                        height={90}
                        class="h-24 w-full object-contain transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105"
                    />
                
                    <Image
                        src="/LogisticsHackathon/communities/github.png"
                        alt="GitHub"
                        width={180}
                        height={90}
                        class="h-24 w-full object-contain transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105"
                    />

                    <Image
                        src="/LogisticsHackathon/communities/Notion_app_logo.png"
                        alt="Notion"
                        width={180}
                        height={90}
                        class="h-24 w-full object-contain transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105"
                    />


            </div>
        </div>
        
        <p class="mt-10 text-lg text-gray-300">
            ¡Agradecemos sinceramente a todas nuestras comunidades!
        </p>

    </div>
</section>